{
  "stem": "1677.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "There is my wooden leg hanging over there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And they said, that stays in the train for the German Wehrmacht-- the sons of the fathers is whom he fought for Kaiser and fatherland.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And they put out a blanket and made him jump into the blanket.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And they shot him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "So that was the end of Paul Haas in my life.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I realized that this is a major crime, and I thought-- I knew that there was in the Hague a Supreme Court-- that I knew.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I made a little-- in my memory-- and I thought-- but I didn't budge.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I didn't cry.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I didn't-- my mother-- my mother was sent to the site with women and her two children.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they was in their smart leather coat, and then with a big, huge torch.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he shone into our faces for a about-- dismal fraction of a second.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And that was night.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Everything in Auschwitz happened at night.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "During the day, we slept.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And with that, he decided right, left, right, left, right-- for the-- how could he judge?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We all-- everybody was strained.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Everybody-- I was a strong girl.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So he sent me to the right, and my mother and my little sister, who was 13, to the left.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I was there amongst all these strange, hysterical women, hiding their babies, screaming their head off, completely out of their mind.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I thought, no.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "This is not for me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I go with my mother, wherever she goes.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "That was again to-- that my needs of protection, I guess.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I went away and marched myself to the left side.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I called, [NON-ENGLISH] to my sister.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I-- we had sailor-- matching sailor coats with golden buttons.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
